<list>
<listItem>
<list>
<listItem>
<sentence type="quasi"><enclosedCharacter description="○">２</enclosedCharacter>‐３５　大<sampling type="start" />学</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<figureBlock>
<figure>
</figure>
<caption>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　両手の人さし指で頭上に<ruby rubyText="かく">角</ruby><ruby rubyText="ぼう">帽</ruby>を形どる。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</caption>
</figureBlock>
</listItem>
</list>
</listItem>
<listItem>
<sentence type="quasi">６１　試験Ａ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<figureBlock>
<figure>
</figure>
<caption>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　両手の親指を立て、交互に上下させる。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</caption>
</figureBlock>
</listItem>
<listItem>
<sentence type="quasi">６２　試験Ｂ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<figureBlock>
<figure>
</figure>
<caption>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　握った両手を交差させひねる。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　<quote>「試す」</quote><quote>「テスト」</quote><quote>「研究」</quote>などにも用いる。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</caption>
</figureBlock>
</listItem>
<listItem>
<sentence type="quasi">６３　合格</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<figureBlock>
<figure>
</figure>
<caption>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　右手を絵のようにして、左手の上にあげる。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</caption>
</figureBlock>
</listItem>
<listItem>
<sentence type="quasi">６４　不合格</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<figureBlock>
<figure>
</figure>
<caption>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　右手を絵のようにして、左手の下へ下げる。</sentence>
<sentence><quote>「落ちる」</quote><quote>「<ruby rubyText="ぼつ">没</ruby><ruby rubyText="らく">落</ruby>」</quote>の意にもつかう。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</caption>
</figureBlock>
</listItem>
<listItem>
<sentence type="quasi">授業</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<list>
<listItem>
<sentence type="quasi"><enclosedCharacter description="○">１</enclosedCharacter>‐２３　勉強</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<figureBlock>
<figure>
</figure>
<caption>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　両手で本を開き読むさま。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</caption>
</figureBlock>
</listItem>
<listItem>
<sentence type="quasi"><enclosedCharacter description="○">２</enclosedCharacter>‐１３　教える</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<figureBlock>
<figure>
</figure>
<caption>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　人さし指を出し前方に二度はねる。</sentence>
<sentence>指さし教える意。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</caption>
</figureBlock>
</listItem>
</list>
</listItem>
<listItem>
<sentence type="quasi">同窓会</sentence>
