<list>
<listItem>
<sentence type="quasi"><enclosedCharacter description="○">１</enclosedCharacter>‐２９　同窓</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<figureBlock>
<figure>
</figure>
<caption>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　絵のようにつまんだ両手を矢印のように動かす。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</caption>
</figureBlock>
</listItem>
<listItem>
<sentence type="quasi"><enclosedCharacter description="○">２</enclosedCharacter>‐４２　会</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<figureBlock>
<figure>
</figure>
<caption>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　両手指を全部立て絵のように動作する。</sentence>
<sentence><quote>「人びとが集まる」</quote><quote>「集会」</quote>などにもつかう。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</caption>
</figureBlock>
</listItem>
</list>
</listItem>
<listItem>
