<listItem>
<sentence type="quasi"><enclosedCharacter description="○">２</enclosedCharacter>‐６６　礼</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<figureBlock>
<figure>
</figure>
<caption>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　立てた両手指を下へ。</sentence>
<sentence>人びとが頭を下げる動作から<ruby rubyText="けい">形</ruby><ruby rubyText="しょう">象</ruby><ruby rubyText="か">化</ruby>したもの。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</caption>
</figureBlock>
</listItem>
</list>
</listItem>
<listItem>
<sentence type="quasi">６７　英語</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<figureBlock>
<figure>
</figure>
<caption>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　えんぴつで英字を書くさま。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</caption>
</figureBlock>
</listItem>
<listItem>
<sentence type="quasi">６８　道徳</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<figureBlock>
<figure>
</figure>
<caption>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　両手を上に向けて握り、小指の側を二、三度合わす。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　<quote>「<ruby rubyText="しゅう">修</ruby><ruby rubyText="しん">身</ruby>」</quote><quote>「<ruby rubyText="れい">礼</ruby><ruby rubyText="ぎ">儀</ruby>」</quote><quote>「エチケット」</quote>などにもつかう。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</caption>
</figureBlock>
</listItem>
<listItem>
<sentence type="quasi">６９　社会</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<figureBlock>
<figure>
</figure>
<caption>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　絵のように両手で指文字<quote>「ヤ」</quote>を作り同時にぐるっと内側にまわす。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</caption>
</figureBlock>
</listItem>
<listItem>
